OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMinister describes         
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F'horrific' accounts of SAS 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fwar crimes                 
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Veterans minister Johnny Mercer has    
OL,6, told a public inquiry he heard         
OL,7, "horrific" accounts from former members
OL,8, of Afghan special forces of the SAS    
OL,9, killing unarmed detainees and children.
OL,11,FAsked by the chair of the inquiry to   
OL,12,Fclarify that he was describing         
OL,13,F"allegations of straight murder" by the
OL,14,FSAS, Mr Mercer replied, "Yes."         
OL,16,FBBC Panorama reported this week that UK
OL,17,FSpecial Forces had blocked Afghan      
OL,18,Fspecial forces, known as the "Triples",
OL,19,Ffrom relocating to the UK after the    
OL,20,FTaliban swept back to power in 2021.   
